==English==

===Etymology===
Pref. a- + loud.

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ʌˈlaʊd/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aʊd|-aʊd]]

===Adverb===
'''aloud'''

# With a loud voice, or great noise; loudly; audibly.
# Audible, as opposed to silent, as in speaking aloud rather than thinking thoughts privately.

====Translations====
*Finnish: ääneen
*Telugu: [[బిగ్గరగా]] (biggaragaa), [[ఎలుగెత్తి]] (elugetti)

